name: Naruto Uzumaki
description: A determined shinobi from the Hidden Leaf Village and the jinchuriki of the Nine-Tails. Naruto is known for his iron will, exuberant personality, and his 'Never Give Up' ninja way.

mainSkill.name: Rasengan
mainSkill.description: A spiraling sphere of chakra held in the hand that grinds into opponents, causing severe internal damage and launching them backward.

secondarySkill.name: Multi Shadow Clone Jutsu
secondarySkill.description: Creates hundreds of solid physical duplicates to overwhelm enemies, scout, or speed up training through shared experience.

justifications.hp: Uzumaki lineage grants exceptional life force and resilience, well above average shinobi.
justifications.str: Physically strong enough to trade blows with enhanced ninja, but lacks the crushing power of Sage Mode.
justifications.def: Standard shinobi durability; vulnerable to piercing attacks but highly resilient to blunt trauma.
justifications.sta: Even in base, his natural chakra reserves are massive (stated to be 4x that of an elite Jonin like Kakashi).
justifications.sp_atk: The Rasengan is a powerful A-rank jutsu capable of grinding through stone and steel.
justifications.int: While academically poor, his combat creativity and ability to adapt on the fly are genius-level.
justifications.spd: Fast movement speed typical of a high-level shinobi, capable of blurring eyesight.
justifications.atk_spd: Good reflexes honed by constant training, though he often relies on clones to bait attacks.

mainSkill.name: Tailed Beast Bomb
mainSkill.description: Compresses positive and negative chakra into a super-heavy sphere that detonates with the force of a nuclear explosion, capable of erasing mountains.

secondarySkill.name: Kurama Avatar
secondarySkill.description: Manifests the full size and power of the Nine-Tails as a translucent golden energy construct, granting immense physical strength and defense.

justifications.hp: The chakra shroud acts as a constant regenerative buffer, allowing him to survive catastrophic impacts.
justifications.str: In this form, he can deflect other Tailed Beasts' attacks and shatter massive rock formations with physical strikes.
justifications.def: The golden cloak is highly resistant to extreme heat and crushing force, acting as energized armor.
justifications.sta: Possesses the combined chakra of an Uzumaki and the strongest Tailed Beast, effectively fighting for days without fatigue.
justifications.sp_atk: His Tailed Beast Bomb is a Continental-level threat, capable of altering maps and vaporizing landscapes.
justifications.int: Displays high-speed tactical processing and the ability to coordinate entire armies through chakra sharing.
justifications.spd: Matches the 'Yellow Flash' in raw speed, moving faster than the eye can track across battlefields.
justifications.atk_spd: Reacts to attacks moving at lightning speeds and can intercept projectiles instantly.

name: Kakashi Hatake
description: A legendary Jonin of Konoha and the Sixth Hokage. Famed for his use of the Sharingan to copy over a thousand jutsu, he is a tactical genius who combines elite elemental ninjutsu with precision assassinations.

mainSkill.name: Raikiri (Lightning Cutter)
mainSkill.description: Concentrates a massive amount of lightning chakra into the hand for a high-speed, piercing thrust capable of cutting through lightning itself.

secondarySkill.name: Kamui
secondarySkill.description: Uses the Mangekyou Sharingan to create a spatial barrier, warping targets or attacks into a separate dimension.

justifications.hp: Resilient shinobi physique, but lacks regenerative traits or massive durability.
justifications.str: Enhanced by chakra flow, capable of contending with strong taijutsu users.
justifications.def: Relies on substitution and evasion; standard flak jacket protection.
justifications.sta: Chakra reserves are notoriously limited compared to powerhouses like Naruto.
justifications.sp_atk: Raikiri and elemental mastery allow for catastrophic damage output.
justifications.int: A prodigy and strategic genius, capable of analyzing enemies instantly.
justifications.spd: Master of the Body Flicker technique, moving faster than the eye can track.
justifications.atk_spd: Sharingan allows him to perceive and react to attacks that are otherwise too fast for humans.

name: Killer Bee
description: The Jinchriki of the Eight-Tails (Gyki) from Kumogakure and brother to the Fourth Raikage. A master swordsman who wields seven blades at once and a rapper at heart, he possesses immense physical strength and perfect control over his Tailed Beast.

mainSkill.name: Lightning Release: Lariat
mainSkill.description: A high-speed charging attack where Bee cloaks himself in chakra and strikes the opponent's neck/chest with his arm, capable of tearing targets apart.

secondarySkill.name: Tailed Beast Ball
secondarySkill.description: Compresses positive and negative chakra into a dense sphere that is fired as a devastating beam or explosive projectile.

justifications.hp: Enhanced vitality from Gyki allows him to survive lethal injuries.
justifications.str: Immense physical power; can wrestle Tailed Beasts and match the Raikage.
justifications.def: Version 2 Chakra Cloak provides heavy defense against high-level jutsu.
justifications.sta: Near-inexhaustible chakra reserves characteristic of a perfect Jinchriki.
justifications.sp_atk: Tailed Beast Bomb is a catastrophic attack capable of vaporizing mountains.
justifications.int: Deceptively smart in combat; uses unorthodox tactics to confuse geniuses.
justifications.spd: Extremely fast; capable of intercepting Minato Namikaze mid-attack.
justifications.atk_spd: His 7-sword style (Acrobat) overwhelms the Sharingan's predictive abilities.

name: Pain
description: The visible leader of the Akatsuki and wielder of the Rinnegan. Operating through the Six Paths of Painreanimated corpses controlled remotely by Nagato Uzumakihe seeks to bring peace to the world through the ultimate experience of suffering and fear.

mainSkill.name: Shinra Tensei (Almighty Push)
mainSkill.description: Manipulates repulsive gravity to blast away all surrounding matter and attacks. At maximum output, it can flatten an entire major city in seconds.

secondarySkill.name: Chibaku Tensei (Planetary Devastation)
secondarySkill.description: Creates a black gravity sphere that pulls all surrounding earth, debris, and enemies into it, crushing them inside a newly formed moon-like satellite.

justifications.hp: The bodies are durable corpses, but the Deva Path has limits before needing restoration.
justifications.str: Enhanced physical capabilities, able to block Sage Mode strikes, but relies mostly on powers.
justifications.def: Can repel almost any physical or ninjutsu attack via Shinra Tensei or Preta Path absorption.
justifications.sta: Nagato's Uzumaki lineage provides near-monstrous chakra reserves to fuel the Rinnegan.
justifications.sp_atk: Capable of leveling Konoha in a single blow; represents a Catastrophic city-level threat.
justifications.int: Controls six bodies simultaneously with shared vision; a tactical genius.
justifications.spd: Can fly and move at high speeds, keeping up with the fastest shinobi.
justifications.atk_spd: Shared field of vision allows for near-perfect reaction times to blindsides.

name: Kaguya Otsutsuki
description: The first wielder of chakra on Earth and the mother of the Sage of Six Paths. An ancient celestial being who consumed the fruit of the God Tree, she possesses power that transcends ninjutsu, capable of shifting dimensions and unmaking the world.

mainSkill.name: All-Killing Ash Bones
mainSkill.description: Hardened bone projectiles fired from the palms. Upon contact, the target's molecular structure is dismantled, turning them to ash instantly.

secondarySkill.name: Amenominaka
secondarySkill.description: Instantly rewrites reality to shift herself and everyone around her into one of her six dimensions (Lava, Ice, Gravity, Acid, Desert, or Core).

justifications.hp: Essentially immortal; can regenerate from almost anything and requires planetary-level sealing to stop.
justifications.str: Her chakra arms and physical strikes can shatter a Perfect Susanoo with ease.
justifications.def: Absorbs all ninjutsu; physical attacks simply bounce off unless imbued with Six Paths power.
justifications.sta: Possesses near-infinite chakra as the source of all chakra; creates dimensions without exhaustion.
justifications.sp_atk: Her Expansive Truth-Seeking Ball is capable of obliterating an entire space-time (Solar System level).
justifications.int: While ancient, she relies heavily on Black Zetsu for strategy and is easily distracted by unorthodox tactics.
justifications.spd: Moves instantaneously within her dimensions; reactions are god-tier.
justifications.atk_spd: Byakugan gives her near 360-degree vision and pre-cognitive reaction capabilities.

name: The Mandalorian
description: A battle-hardened bounty hunter and formidable warrior who lives by the strict code of the 'Children of the Watch'. Once a lone gunfighter, his life changed when he became the guardian of the Force-sensitive child, Grogu.

mainSkill.name: Whistling Birds
mainSkill.description: Deploys a salvo of tiny, homing Beskar darts that target multiple enemies simultaneously, delivering lethal micro-explosions.

secondarySkill.name: Amban Phase-Pulse
secondarySkill.description: Fires a long-range disruptor blast that disintegrates targets on a molecular level or delivers a high-voltage shock in melee.

justifications.hp: Human biology enhanced by survival training, but relies heavily on his suit to survive fatal blows.
justifications.str: Superhuman feats including overpowering Droids and grappling with large alien beasts.
justifications.def: Beskar plating is nearly indestructible, no-selling heavy blaster fire and lightsaber strikes (Urban tier protection).
justifications.sta: High-level operative endurance capable of multi-day tracking and prolonged firefights.
justifications.sp_atk: Arsenal includes disintegrators, flamethrowers, and explosives capable of destroying tanks.
justifications.int: Expert tactician and 'Supercomputer' level combat simulation; can adapt to unfamiliar tech and alien cultures.
justifications.spd: Human running speed, significantly increased by a Z-6 jetpack for rapid repositioning.
justifications.atk_spd: Elite reaction time; can outdraw multiple hunters and dodge incoming projectiles.

name: Anakin Skywalker
description: The newly christened Sith Apprentice after the fall of the Jedi Order. Fueled by raw emotion, desperation, and the Dark Side, he possesses all the agility of his youth combined with a newfound, savage brutality.

mainSkill.name: Form V: Djem So
mainSkill.description: A relentless onslaught of heavy-handed lightsaber strikes designed to batter through defenses and physically dominate the opponent.

secondarySkill.name: Force Choke
secondarySkill.description: Channels the Dark Side to crush the target's throat remotely, stunning them and dealing continuous damage.

justifications.hp: Superhuman resilience fueled by rage, though still biologically mortal and susceptible to catastrophic injury.
justifications.str: Enhanced by his cybernetic arm and the Force, capable of overpowering seasoned Jedi Masters in lock-ups.
justifications.def: Wears standard Jedi robes offering minimal physical protection; relies entirely on parrying and offense.
justifications.sta: Dark Side fervor allows him to fight for days (e.g., Operation Knightfall) without fatigue.
justifications.sp_atk: Possesses the highest raw Force potential in history; his telekinesis is catastrophic in scale.
justifications.int: A brilliant combat tactician, but his judgment is currently clouded by arrogance and emotional instability.
justifications.spd: At his physical peak; uses Force jumps and dashes for high-speed acrobatics (unlike his later suited self).
justifications.atk_spd: Pre-cognitive reflexes allow him to react to attacks before they happen, moving in a blur.

mainSkill.name: Titanic Force Crush
mainSkill.description: Channels immense telekinetic pressure to crumple heavy durasteel plating, implode walkers (AT-ATs), or crush the internal organs of leviathans.

secondarySkill.name: Sith Rage
secondarySkill.description: A self-buff that converts pain and hatred into raw physical power and durability, allowing him to ignore critical damage.

justifications.hp: Nearly unkillable; survives electrocution, vacuum, ocean pressure, and being crushed by walkers.
justifications.str: Cosmic tier lifting strength; ripped a dimensional rift open and held back an ocean (Fallen Order).
justifications.def: Beskar-reinforced armor combined with Force Barriers allows him to tank orbital bombardment and lava.
justifications.sta: Fueled by the Dark Side; can fight for days without rest, limited only by his suit's life support.
justifications.sp_atk: Planetary threat; capable of devastating telekinetic feats that rival natural disasters.
justifications.int: A cold, calculating genius who leads the Imperial Navy and anticipates enemy movements perfectly.
justifications.spd: Physically slow and deliberate in movement, relying on an imposing, horror-movie-like advance.
justifications.atk_spd: Catastrophic reflexes; precognition allows him to block omni-directional fire and speed-blitz masters.

justifications.hp: High endurance and resilience, though lacks the mechanical durability of his later armored form.
justifications.str: Superhuman physical strength, further augmented by his cybernetic right arm and Force-enhanced strikes.
justifications.def: Relies on his lightsaber and agility; his robes offer no protection against physical or energy attacks.
justifications.sta: Extreme stamina driven by 'Sith Rage', allowing him to fight through the Siege of the Jedi Temple without rest.
justifications.sp_atk: Terrifying Force potential; capable of devastating telekinetic waves and crushing heavy machinery.
justifications.int: A brilliant but impulsive tactician; currently clouded by intense rage and emotional instability.
justifications.spd: Urban tier mobility; uses Force-enhanced leaps and dashes to close gaps and overwhelm opponents.
justifications.atk_spd: Near-precognitive reaction speeds; his Djem So lightsaber strikes are a blur of high-velocity kinetic force.

name: Captain America
description: The First Avenger. A recipient of the Super Soldier Serum, Steve Rogers possesses peak human potential and unwavering moral fortitude. Armed with his indestructible Vibranium shield, he leads Earth's mightiest heroes against any threat.

mainSkill.name: Shield Throw
mainSkill.description: Hurls the Vibranium shield with perfect geometric precision, ricocheting off multiple enemies or surfaces before returning to his hand.

secondarySkill.name: Vibranium Bulwark
secondarySkill.description: Raises the shield to absorb kinetic energy and energy blasts, negating incoming damage and creating a shockwave upon impact.

justifications.hp: Superhuman durability allowing him to survive falls from elevators and hits from Winter Soldier's arm.
justifications.str: Enhanced strength (Urban tier low-end); famously held back a taking-off helicopter and throws motorcycles.
justifications.def: His Vibranium shield is Catastrophic tier; it can withstand blows from Mjolnir and Thanos's blade.
justifications.sta: Serum prevents fatigue toxins from building up; he can literally 'do this all day'.
justifications.sp_atk: Lacks inherent energy projection; relies entirely on physical physics calculations with the shield.
justifications.int: Master tactician and field leader; adapts to alien technology and magic instantly in combat scenarios.
justifications.spd: Runs at speeds exceeding 60 mph; consistently outpaces traffic and other heroes on foot.
justifications.atk_spd: Elite reflexes allow him to dodge bullets and block energy beams after they are fired.
